description: We are selling our fun and collectible 1955 Wizard Classic boat. Fiberglass and Teak boat. Comes with original sales receipt, brochure. It has been restored but it also has been used for fishing, cruising, swimming and all lake fun with the kids It is a boat that turns heads. It's classic look will only increase in value. As most other boats depreciate, this one will not. Cruise it, use it, enjoy it knowing that it is an investment rather than something that will not hold its value. I am negotiable on price.  I would like for another family to enjoy. Come check it out and make an offer. It is a great boat, runs great. Trailer is included and in good shape. The boat is very light and easy to tow.
